{"tid":885794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter:抓緊中國企業向海外擴張時機","createTime":"2018-11-01T15:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T15:59:29.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2203b92a72a130ba99a7e306634f02218fb130a4","tid":885794,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:11:56.000Z","msg":"社交媒體平台Twitter首席客戶官Matt Derella對財新網表示，亞太地區是Twitter全球增長的重要引擎，而中國市場亦愈來愈重要。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，今年該公司在中國的活動頻繁，現時是抓緊中國企業向海外擴張的好時機。<br />\n<br />\nMatt Derella指出，該公司高度重視中國市場，惟未有透露來自中國市場的收入佔比。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1981486/Twitter%3A%E6%8A%93%E7%B7%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%90%91%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5%E6%99%82%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1981486%2FTwitter%253A%25E6%258A%2593%25E7%25B7%258A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%25A9%259F&d=rhwCuyOkgID7OebO1yMOFsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0978cdb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1981486/Twitter%3A%E6%8A%93%E7%B7%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%90%91%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5%E6%99%82%E6%A9%9F</a>"},{"pid":"9ef0f1172226b7ab89fd82bbec515ca71b902902","tid":885794,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲奶共咁撚弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e58fb274d8c5a2cbdfbf13529ba4d2559a9169","tid":885794,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"之前仲叫人玩twitter...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}